00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,850
I'm not sure.

322
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,521
Thank you.

323
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:43,780
- Hey, Melinda.
- Hi.

324
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:46,360
- You look great.
- Uh, hi!

