468
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:59,380
How does that work?
Two bass lines in two different keys?

469
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,540
Well, it works in my head.

470
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,860
It's all playing in my head.

