My brothers and my parents
and everybody.

501
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:39,980
Everybody.

502
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:42,940
Wow. That sounds like
such a wonderful childhood.

503
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:44,644
Yeah, it was really nice...

504
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:46,980
