00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:55,049
You know, like, um...

508
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:59,780
There's a spanking. You know that sound?

509
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,380
You know a certain kind of spanking...

510
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,084
and it sounds like a...
you know, like...

