1425
01:28:29,760 --> 01:28:32,580
I have been writing lyrics professionally
since I was 14 years old.

1426
01:28:32,680 --> 01:28:36,180
- I don't need to be here.
- Good, then go! Please.

1427
01:28:36,280 --> 01:28:39,060
It's safer for everyone on the deep end!

1428
01:28:39,160 --> 01:28:41,900
We have got to finish this album
and we are not going to do it this way.

1429
01:28:42,000 --> 01:28:43,420
Not in these fragments!

1430
01:28:43,520 --> 01:28:45,020
Breaking it up and moving us all around.

1431
01:28:45,120 --> 01:28:47,180
The house is bugged.

1432
01:28:47,280 --> 01:28:49,420
